  "body": "*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: SEND command is not fully integrated with Wallet \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nerror “Amount should be specified” is shown if send ether from wallet\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Sync the app\r\n- Request some ETH\r\n- Add any contact to contact list ( i was using the other one I have on my device)\r\n- Go to wallet\r\n- click Open wallet\r\n- enter any appropriate amount in SEND field and click SEND button\r\n- select a contact from the contact list\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version:  http://artifacts.status.im:8081/artifactory/pull-requests/im.status.ethereum-7eeb9c.apk\r\n* Operating System: Android 6.0.1\r\n* Video https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B7h1U1joPifRUW8xS1JkMEduY0U\r\n#### Logs\r\n[05-07-2017 logcat.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/1124897/05-07-2017.logcat.txt)\r\n\r\n",
